<content-text><p><b>Packet Tracer Activity</b></p> <p>Use the knowledge and skills presented in this course to troubleshoot network connectivity problems relating to:</p> <p><ul><li> VLAN configuration</li><li> OSPF configuration</li><li> WAN interface configuration</li><li> Access Control List configuration </li></ul></p><p><b>Click the Packet Tracer icon to begin.</b></p></content-text>
